This folder contains all the problem sheets (assignments, tutorials, or practice problems) from the Basic Electronics course, along with my own detailed solutions.

## Structure
- The original sheet (usually in PDF format)
- My handwritten or typed solutions

## Topics Covered
The sheets cover:
- Diode circuits and rectifiers
- Clipping/clamping applications
- BJT biasing and small-signal models
- FET biasing and amplifier basics
- Basic analog applications


